headline: Labcorp to Webcast Its Annual Meeting of Shareholders May 15
summary: Labcorp (NYSE: LH), a global leader of innovative and comprehensive laboratory services, today announced that its Annual Meeting of Shareholders will be webcast live on May 15 at 9:00 a.m. ET and can be viewed online on the Labcorp Investor Relations website. An archived replay of the webcast will be available for one year.
